reviewText: Funny, raw, and overall great independent movie. Hilarious from start to end. Even the commentary track was a hoot. Talk about a "Dark Comedy"

While not for everyone, this is a really funny film if you like b-grade horror and/or comedy. Combining grindhouse style with gross out comedy, director Tom Martino doesn't pull any punches and doesn't give a f*** if you like it or not.
